title.en: Tensei Reijou, Kekkon no Susume - Akujo ga Gimai no Kawari ni Totsuidanara
Seirei Mahou ga Tsukaenai Munou da to Konyaku Hakisareta no de, Gimai no Dorei ni Naru Yori Tsuihou wo Erabimashita
"Omae ga Kawari ni Shine" to Iwareta Watashi. Imouto no Migawari ni Reikoku na Henkyou Haku no Moto e Totsugi, Shiawase wo Teniireru
Gaikotsu Ou to Migawari no Oujo - Luna to Okubyou na Ousama
Ryuushi no Hanayome - Shinryoku no Otome wa Seiryuu no Shugosha ni Aisareru
Botsuraku Reijou na no ni Dai 2 Ouji ni Kyuukonsaretemasu
Kokoro ga Yomeru Oujo wa Konyakusha no Dekiai ni Kizukanai
Nibante no Onna - Utahime to shite no Hokori wo Mune ni, Saigo no Gohoukou wo Itashimasu
Ikenie to shite Surerareta no de, Henkyou Hakke ni Jibun wo Urimasu
Kore kara Shiawase ni narimasu! Shiitagerare Reijou desu ga Tekitaikoku no Koushaku-sama ni Naze ka Dekiaisaretemasu
Tsuihousareta Rakudai Majo wa Wakaki Kishi ni Koi wo suru
Mahou wa Koi ni Hen Shiteru
Hakushaku Reijou ni Natte Ojou-sama no Kekkon wo Buchikowashimasu!
Sue Oujo no Koshire - Sono Kage de Hamerare, Tsukai Suterareta Oujo no Kagemusha no Shoujo ga Jibun no Shiawase wo Tsukamu made
"Jimide Tsumaranai" to Suterareta no de, Jimichi ni Renkinjutsushi wo Mezashimasu!
Suterare Hanayome no Saikon - Koori no Henkyou Haku wa Saiai o Chikau
